---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tentang" description="Profil tentang Fatahilah Miftahul Rahman, lulusan SMK Patriot Pituruh jurusan TKJ (2026), Juara 1 LKS IT Network System Administration, serta praktisi AI Prompt Engineering.">
  <section class="about-section container section-py">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-badge">
        <span class="badge font-mono" data-i18n="nav.about">Tentang</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-heading" data-i18n="about.title">About Me & Profil Profesional</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle" data-i18n="about.subtitle">
        Memadukan keahlian administrasi jaringan & sistem server dengan inovasi otomatisasi berbasis AI Prompt Engineering.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Profile Section -->
    <div class="hero-profile-card glass-card">
      <div class="hero-profile-info">
        <span class="badge badge-primary font-mono" data-i18n="about.profile.badge">IT Network & System Administration</span>
        <h2 class="hero-name font-heading">Fatahilah Miftahul Rahman</h2>
        <p class="hero-desc" data-i18n="about.profile.desc">
          Connecting the future, one network at a time. Spesialis infrastruktur jaringan, konfigurasi server Linux/Windows, serta otomatisasi berbasis AI Prompt Engineering.
        </p>
        <div class="status-indicator">
          <span class="status-dot"></span>
          <span class="status-text font-mono" data-i18n="about.profile.status">Siap Kerja & Berkembang di Industri IT (Lulusan 2026)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-profile-photo">
        <div class="avatar-ring">
          <img src="https://cdn.fatahmr.my.id/portfolio/assets/profile.webp" alt="Foto Profil Fatahilah Miftahul Rahman" width="160" height="160" class="avatar-img" fetchpriority="high" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main About Grid -->
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Left Column: Biography -->
      <div class="about-bio glass-card">
        <h2 class="bio-heading font-heading" data-i18n="about.bio.heading">Latar Belakang & Visi Teknologi</h2>
        <div class="bio-content">
          <p data-i18n="about.bio.p1">
            Saya lulusan SMK Patriot Pituruh jurusan Teknik Komputer dan Jaringan (2026) dengan spesialisasi di bidang IT Network & System Administration. Prestasi terbaik saya adalah meraih Juara 1 pada Lomba Kompetensi Siswa (LKS) SMK tingkat Kabupaten Purworejo di bidang IT Network System Administration.
          </p>
          <p data-i18n="about.bio.p2">
            Saat ini, saya tidak hanya fokus pada infrastruktur jaringan dan manajemen server, tetapi juga mendalami AI Prompt Engineering. Saya melihat potensi besar AI untuk mengotomatisasi skrip jaringan dan troubleshooting sistem, sehingga pekerjaan di industri bisa menjadi lebih efisien, cepat, dan aman.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bio-actions">
          <a href="/experience" class="btn-primary" data-i18n="about.bio.btn.exp">Lihat Pengalaman →</a>
          <a href="/skills" class="btn-secondary" data-i18n="about.bio.btn.skills">Daftar Keahlian Teknis →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Meta Info & Achievement Cards -->
      <div class="about-meta">
        <!-- Pendidikan Card -->
        <div class="meta-card glass-card">
          <div class="meta-icon font-mono" data-i18n="about.meta.edu.label">🎓 Pendidikan</div>
          <h3 class="meta-title font-heading">SMK Patriot Pituruh</h3>
          <p class="meta-val font-mono" data-i18n="about.meta.edu.val">Teknik Komputer dan Jaringan (TKJ)</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tahun Lulus Card -->
        <div class="meta-card glass-card">
          <div class="meta-icon font-mono" data-i18n="about.meta.year.label">📅 Tahun Lulus</div>
          <h3 class="meta-title font-heading">2026</h3>
          <p class="meta-val font-mono" data-i18n="about.meta.year.val">Siap Kerja &amp; Berkembang di Industri IT</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Prestasi LKS Featured Card -->
        <div class="achievement-card glass-card">
          <div class="achievement-badge font-mono badge badge-gold" data-i18n="about.meta.achieve.label">🏆 Prestasi</div>
          <h3 class="achievement-title font-heading" data-i18n="about.meta.achieve.title">Lomba Kompetensi Siswa (LKS) SMK</h3>
          <div class="achievement-val font-mono" data-i18n="about.meta.achieve.val">Juara I</div>
          <p class="achievement-desc font-mono" data-i18n="about.meta.achieve.desc" data-i18n-html="true">IT Network System Administration<br>Tingkat Kabupaten Purworejo, 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Core Philosophy / Focus Areas -->
    <div class="focus-areas">
      <div class="focus-header">
        <h2 class="font-heading focus-main-title" data-i18n="about.focus.heading">Fokus & Kompetensi Utama</h2>
        <p class="focus-subtitle" data-i18n="about.focus.subtitle">Tiga pilar utama yang menjadi pondasi keahlian teknis saya dalam menyelesaikan tantangan IT modern.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-grid">
        <div class="focus-item glass-card">
          <span class="focus-num font-mono">01</span>
          <h3 class="focus-title font-heading" data-i18n="about.focus.item1.title">Network Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="focus-desc" data-i18n="about.focus.item1.desc">Perancangan dan pengamanan topologi jaringan LAN, WLAN, VLAN, routing, serta konfigurasi RouterBoard MikroTik & Cisco.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-item glass-card">
          <span class="focus-num font-mono">02</span>
          <h3 class="focus-title font-heading" data-i18n="about.focus.item2.title">Server Administration</h3>
          <p class="focus-desc" data-i18n="about.focus.item2.desc">Instalasi & optimalisasi Linux Debian Server (DNS, Web Server Nginx/Apache, DHCP, Nftables Firewall, dan High Availability HAProxy).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-item glass-card">
          <span class="focus-num font-mono">03</span>
          <h3 class="focus-title font-heading" data-i18n="about.focus.item3.title">AI Prompt Engineering</h3>
          <p class="focus-desc" data-i18n="about.focus.item3.desc">Pemanfaatan Large Language Models (LLM) untuk pembuatan otomatisasi skrip administrasi jaringan dan percepatan analisis troubleshooting.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Section Header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }
  .section-badge {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  /* Hero Profile Card */
  .hero-profile-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card) 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.06) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    padding: 40px 48px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .hero-profile-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 62ch;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .status-indicator {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: #22c55e;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px #22c55e;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .status-text {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .hero-profile-photo {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .avatar-ring {
    width: 168px;
    height: 168px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    padding: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-accent));
    box-shadow: 0 0 35px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.35);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .avatar-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
  }

  /* Main About Grid */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: stretch;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .about-bio {
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .bio-heading {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .bio-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .bio-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .bio-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    padding-top: 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Meta & Achievement Column */
  .about-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .meta-card,
  .achievement-card {
    padding: 24px 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .meta-card:hover,
  .achievement-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .meta-icon {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .meta-title,
  .achievement-title {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
  }

  .meta-val {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .achievement-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card) 0%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.06) 100%);
  }

  .achievement-badge {
    align-self: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .achievement-val {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin: 4px 0 8px 0;
  }

  .achievement-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Focus Areas */
  .focus-areas {
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding-top: 24px;
  }

  .focus-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  .focus-main-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .focus-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .focus-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .focus-item {
    padding: 32px 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .focus-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md), var(--shadow-glow);
  }

  .focus-num {
    display: inline-block;
    align-self: flex-start;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .focus-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-foreground);
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }

  .focus-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Responsive Design Scale (`refactoring-ui` breakpoints) */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .focus-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-profile-card {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 24px;
      gap: 28px;
    }
    .hero-profile-info {
      align-items: center;
    }
    .about-bio {
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }
    .bio-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .bio-actions .btn-primary,
    .bio-actions .btn-secondary {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .focus-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .focus-item {
      padding: 26px 22px;
    }
  }
</style>
